          "reviewBody": "Hi all..\nI am sharing this from my bottom of my heart.. Euro kids Madurawada branch is located in a peaceful nature surrounded place.. School building is safe and secured for kids to learn and play. Kids are taken care very well.. Right from teachers to aaya amma everyone is very friendly and giving atmost care.. My son love this school a lot.. Everyday he was very much eager to go to school.. Special thanks to Poornima mam, She was my sons class teacher, I could see more development in my son's handwriting, thinking aspect, vocabulary etc.. Thanks to Bhavni mam and all other teachers.. Keep up the good work... I would strongly recommend this school for preschool.. No complaints,  Highly satisfied ❤️❤️❤️",
