            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I am a Euro Parent. We shifted to Vishakhapatnam recently this year and found the best school for our Son to enroll him in Nursery. Everything is just best about this school, but the most best part is the teachers of the school. They are extremely polite and soft-spoken. The Principal of the school Bhavani Mam is so cooperative and will address all our problem with utmost patience. I strongly recommend this preschool as they are specialized in that and such school encourages toddlers to attend the school and create love for the school. The best pre school with best infrastructure any pre school parent can ask for.",
          "publisher": {
